<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/NutritionCoaching.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/home_style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="nutrition-coaching-header">
        <h1>Personalized Nutrition Coaching</h1>
        <p>Get expert advice and a customized meal plan to fuel your fitness journey!</p>
    </header>

    <section class="nutrition-coaching-info container my-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
                <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/img/f710044bf79a4b1f5d8b085e5e5d9711_M.jpg")"
                     alt="Nutrition Coaching"
                     class="img-fluid rounded"
                     style="max-height: 400px; object-fit: cover; width: 100%;">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>What is Nutrition Coaching?</h2>
                <p>
                    Our nutrition coaching program is designed to help you build a healthy relationship with food.
                    Whether your goal is weight loss, muscle gain, or overall wellness, our certified nutritionists
                    will create a personalized meal plan and provide ongoing support to ensure you achieve sustainable results.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="nutrition-coaching-benefits">
        <h2>Benefits of Nutrition Coaching</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Personalized meal plans tailored to your goals</li>
            <li>Expert guidance from certified nutritionists</li>
            <li>Improved energy levels and performance</li>
            <li>Long-term sustainable healthy eating habits</li>
            <li>Regular check-ins to track progress and adjust plans</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="nutrition-coaching-cta">
        <p>Ready to take control of your diet?</p>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")" class="btn-cta">Book Your Consultation</a>
    </section>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
